表格账号管理的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('SysUserInfo')
and type = 'U')
drop table SysUserInfo
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: SysUserInfo */
/*==============================================================*/
create table SysUserInfo (
ID int identity(1,1),
UserID char(20) not null,
UserName nvarchar(50) null,
Password nvarchar(50) null,
Sex char(10) null,
Email nvarchar(50) null,
DeptID nchar(10) null,
GroupID varchar(50) null,
IsLock bit null,
LastIP nvarchar(50) null,
aDate datetime null,
mDate datetime null,
cDate datetime null constraint DF_SysUserInfo_cDate default getdate(),
constraint PK_SysUserInfo primary key ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY]
END
go
